      "writtenOn": "2017-07-07T15:57:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Skia enums typically start with a capital letter. And the \"j\" doesn\u0027t seem to add a whole lot. Maybe just call this \"State\"?\n\nAlso, we\u0027ve moved towards using enum classes.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 63,
        "startChar": 9,
        "endLine": 63,
        "endChar": 15
      },
      "revId": "28ed1d604ca0b861631ecf1da6192ea3e3619fcf",
