      "message": "We typically put friends and INHERITED last, so these should be moved up above those two.\n\nAlso, we add spaces to line up the names, so this should look something like:\n\nstd::unique_ptr\u003cSkSwizzler\u003e        fSwizzler;\njstate                             fState;\nvoid*                              fDst;\nsize_t                             fDstRowBytes;\n\nfriend class SkRawCodec;\n\ntypedef SkCodec INHERITED;\n\n(Drats, the formatting did not get preserved in my comment, but all those names beginning with \u0027f\u0027 should line up.)",
